            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Above 3 MeV an electromagnetically separated 99.9% 12C",
                "target on a gold backing was used and which had a",
                "nominal thickness of 116 mu-g/cm2 (or 65 keV) at 6 MeV",
